#: urpm/cli/main.py:756
msgid ""
"Build RPM packages in isolated containers.\n"
"\n"
"Each build runs in a fresh container that is destroyed after completion,\n"
"ensuring a clean build environment. Media and packages are updated\n"
"automatically before building (use --no-update to skip).\n"
"\n"
"Output locations:\n"
"  - .spec files: results go to workspace/RPMS/ and workspace/SRPMS/\n"
"  - .src.rpm files: results go to --output directory (default: ./build-"
"output)\n"
"\n"
"Examples:\n"
"  # Build a spec file (output to ./RPMS/ and ./SRPMS/)\n"
"  urpm build -i mageia:10-build SPECS/foo.spec\n"
"\n"
"  # Build a SRPM (output to ./build-output/foo/)\n"
"  urpm build -i mageia:10-build foo-1.0-1.mga10.src.rpm\n"
"\n"
"  # Build with local dependencies (e.g., libfoo built previously)\n"
"  urpm build -i mageia:10-build SPECS/bar.spec -w 'RPMS/x86_64/libfoo*.rpm'\n"
"\n"
"  # Skip auto-update (image is already up to date)\n"
"  urpm build -i mageia:10-build --no-update SPECS/foo.spec\n"
msgstr ""
"Compile des paquets RPM dans des conteneurs isolés.\n"
"\n"
"Chaque compilation s'exécute dans un conteneur vierge détruit à la fin,\n"
"garantissant un environnement de compilation propre. Les médias et les paquets\n"
"sont mis à jour automatiquement avant la compilation (utilisez --no-update pour ignorer).\n"
"\n"
"Emplacements des résultats :\n"
"  - fichiers .spec : résultats dans workspace/RPMS/ et workspace/SRPMS/\n"
"  - fichiers .src.rpm : résultats dans le répertoire --output (par défaut : ./build-output)\n"
"\n"
"Exemples :\n"
"  # Compiler un fichier spec (sortie dans ./RPMS/ et ./SRPMS/)\n"
"  urpm build -i mageia:10-build SPECS/foo.spec\n"
"\n"
"  # Compiler un SRPM (sortie dans ./build-output/foo/)\n"
"  urpm build -i mageia:10-build foo-1.0-1.mga10.src.rpm\n"
"\n"
"  # Compiler avec des dépendances locales (ex. : libfoo compilée précédemment)\n"
"  urpm build -i mageia:10-build SPECS/bar.spec -w 'RPMS/x86_64/libfoo*.rpm'\n"
"\n"
"  # Ignorer la mise à jour automatique (l'image est déjà à jour)\n"
"  urpm build -i mageia:10-build --no-update SPECS/foo.spec\n"

